The key issues that were causing the infinite loading were:

1. Duplicate code - You had extra code after the initialization function that was causing syntax errors
2. Missing closing braces - There was a stray }, 100); that was breaking the JavaScript
3. Duplicate debug button creation - The debug button was being created twice

Replace the initialization section with the code above, and the app should load properly. The loading screen will disappear once the app is fully initialized and rendered.
